## Key techniques used here

| Technique | Purpose |
|-----------|---------|
| `@Mock` / `@InjectMocks` | Isolate the real service with a fake repository. |
| `when(...).thenReturn/thenAnswer` | Define repository behaviour per test. |
| `thenAnswer` | Simulate DB side effects (ID assignment, echo-back). |
| `ArgumentCaptor` | Inspect the exact object passed to the repository. |
| `verify(..., never())` | Prove a write **did not** happen on error paths. |
| `assertThatThrownBy` | Assert exception type *and* message in one fluent check. |
